toyotama.pwn package¶

Submodules¶

toyotama.pwn.fsa module¶

toyotama.pwn.fsa.fsa_write(target_addr: int, contents: int, nth_stack: int, output=0, sofar=0, offset=0, bits=64)¶

target_addr: The address where the content will be written contents: What you want to write output: The number of characters which executable output sofar: The length of payload so far nth_stack: example

“AAAA%p %p %p…” -> AAAA0x1e 0xf7f6f580 0x804860b 0xf7f6f000 0xf7fbb2f0 (nil) 0x4141d402 -> 7th (0x4141d402)

offset: from this example, offset is 2 (0x4141d402)
